data.text:
Giselle Sarmiento

ACTIVITIES COORDINATOR

activities@apsasdsu.org

Pronouns: She/Her/Hers

Year at SDSU: 3rd

Major: Speech, Language, and Hearing Sciences

Hometown: Chula Vista baby

Ethnicity/Ethnicities I Identify As: Filipino Americaan

FAMS:

2019-2020: PeRfeCtion fam

2020-2021: NuMBer fam

Favorite APSA Memory: Punching cardboard into the trash can with Jalea during FTS WOW :)

Obesessions: Cody Simpson, Michael Buble, Tori Kelly angelic voice, k-dramas, good food, Christmas, 2000's movies, Charmed the show, swimming and going to the beach, and laughing with people

Talents: Daydreaming, overthinking, singing somewhat I guess..

Pet Peeves: I dislike backhanded compliments and when people won't reply to a direct message you send them but will respond in a group chat. I do not like when people make you wait too long in the car when you are picking them up to go somewhere.

Favorite Dessert: red velvet bundt cake

Biggest Accomplishment: After we were done with an activity in Fam Bam I suggested we play duck duck goose to my Fam and shortly after, everyone else started playing :)

Which celebrity (or celebrities) would you like to be roommates with ? Why?
